videos.title: The Grim Captain is Here to Save Standard  Against the Odds
videos.description:
This past weekend I watched The Grim Captain beat Izzet Prowess on camera from the RC and I knew I just had to give it a try myself! What are the odds The Grim Captain is the solution to Standard's Izzet Prowess problem? Let's find out!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
